                            <comment id="41582" author="pjones" created="Sun, 8 Jul 2012 02:56:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Rather than put an incorrect release we can just leave the release fixed field empty and populate it if/when we form concrete plans for a 1.8.9 release.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
