                            <comment id="41564" author="laisiyao" created="Fri, 6 Jul 2012 13:24:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Cory, thanks for your clarification.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="41559" author="spitzcor" created="Fri, 6 Jul 2012 10:47:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Lai, which patch landed?  You marked this bug fixed for 2.3.0, but I don&apos;t see any master patches beyond &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1128&quot; title=&quot;Complete investigation of the LDLM pool shrinker and SLV handling&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1128&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1128&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and that was marked fixed for 2.2.0 and 2.1.2.  change #3138 landed to b1_8 so maybe this ticket should be marked fixed for 1.8.9 instead, if that is possible.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="41554" author="laisiyao" created="Fri, 6 Jul 2012 03:58:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patched landed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="40846" author="laisiyao" created="Tue, 19 Jun 2012 09:21:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The issue &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1128&quot; title=&quot;Complete investigation of the LDLM pool shrinker and SLV handling&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1128&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1128&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; fixed is for ldlm server, that is, it may occur on MGS, MDS and OSS.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="40844" author="ihara" created="Tue, 19 Jun 2012 08:39:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Lai, &lt;br/&gt;
thanks! we will try your backport patch. btw, this problem happened on MDS, does &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1128&quot; title=&quot;Complete investigation of the LDLM pool shrinker and SLV handling&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1128&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1128&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; causes this problem on MDS as well?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="40838" author="laisiyao" created="Tue, 19 Jun 2012 05:03:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This looks to be the same issue in &lt;a href=&quot;http://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1128&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1128&lt;/a&gt;. I&apos;ve backported the fix at: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3138&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3138&lt;/a&gt;. Could you find a way to verify?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
